data.description: Single Story Home located in the Guard Gated Golf Community of Stallion Mountain! 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathroom. Kitchen with Custom Cabinets, Granite Counters,  Breakfast Bar. Top of the Line Appliances will Convey to New Owner.  Open Floor plan with Ceramic Tile throughout and Carpet in the Bedrooms. Front Courtyard as well as a Backyard ready for Entertaining. Not Age Restricted. Easy to show. Come check us out. Luxury Living at it's Best!
